---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Experiencias Exclusivas | Casa L&G">
  <main class="bg-[#0b0707] text-white">
    
    <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 pt-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,_#1a1111_0%,_#0b0707_100%)]"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-sans text-[#C5A059] tracking-[0.6em] text-[10px] md:text-[12px] uppercase mb-6 animate-slide-up">
          El Arte de Vivir el Detalle
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-premium text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none animate-fade-in opacity-0 [animation-fill-mode:forwards] [animation-delay:200ms]">
          EXPERIENCIAS <br/>
          <span class="italic text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F2D184] via-[#C5A059] to-[#8C6D2E]">
            Inolvidables
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-white/50 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 font-light animate-fade-in opacity-0 [animation-fill-mode:forwards] [animation-delay:400ms]">
          Diseñamos emociones y momentos a medida. En Casa L&G, no solo entregamos un detalle; creamos la atmósfera perfecta para celebrar la vida.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wine-cheese text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Noche de Vino & Quesos</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Una selección curada de cepas premium y quesos artesanales, diseñada para una velada de sofisticación absoluta.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-basket-shopping text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Picnic Deluxe</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Llevamos el lujo al aire libre. Un montaje impecable con detalles gourmet para conectar con la naturaleza.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-cake-candles text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Celebraciones Especiales</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Cualquier hito merece un despliegue de elegancia. Personalizamos cada detalle para que tu evento sea único.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Experiencia Aniversario</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">El romance elevado a su máxima expresión. Detalles grabados y atmósferas que cuentan su historia de amor.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-champagne-glasses text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Brunch Exclusivo</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Mañanas radiantes con sabores delicados y burbujas. La forma más elegante de comenzar una celebración.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-[30px] transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-[#C5A059]/30">
          <div class="mb-8 text-[#C5A059] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-utensils text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-premium text-2xl mb-4">Cena Romántica</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Un chef privado, música tenue y un montaje de mesa de revista. La intimidad nunca fue tan lujosa.</p>
          <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-white/5 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/20 transition-colors"></div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 text-center">
      <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-12 py-5 bg-[#C5A059] text-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full transition-transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(197,160,89,0.3)]">
        Cotizar Mi Experiencia VIP
      </a>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { transform: translateY(30px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1s ease-out; }
  .animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 1.5s ease-out forwards; }
  .font-premium { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
</style>